* unnecessary, harmful restriction of speech happens not only under tyrannical states, but even in countries that are considered to be the most free ones
* examples
	* Democrats Join Republicans In Bill Criminalizing Speech Critical Of Israel
		* https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/democrats-join-republicans-in-bill-criminalizing-speech_us_5978bc17e4b0c6616f7ce6d9
	* Ads showing bad female drivers and inept dads banned in UK crackdown on sexist commercials
		* https://edition.cnn.com/2019/06/14/media/uk-gender-stereotypes-advertising-ban-scli-gbr-intl/index.html
	* in much of Europe : the denial [or even the questioning] of the holocaust [and other "crimes against humanity"] is prohibited
